{"abstract": "Mr. Cawley\u2019s MBNA Corporation introduced affinity credit cards, which are tied to sports teams, universities, professional associations and other organizations that inspire consumer loyalty.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/25/business/charles-m-cawley-founder-of-mbna-corp-dies-at-75.html", "snippet": "Mr. Cawley\u2019s MBNA Corporation introduced affinity credit cards, which are tied to sports teams, universities, professional associations and other organizations that inspire consumer loyalty.", "lead_paragraph": "Charles M. Cawley, who founded MBNA Corporation in a supermarket basement, transformed the company into the world\u2019s largest independent credit card issuer, and sold it two decades later to Bank of America for nearly $35 billion, died on Nov. 18 at his home in Camden, Me. He was 75.", "print_section": "B", "print_page": "8", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2015/11/25/business/25cawley-obit-1/25cawley-obit-1-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 504, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2015/11/25/business/25cawley-obit-1/25cawley-obit-1-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 504}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2015/11/25/business/25cawley-obit-1/25cawley-obit-1-jumbo.jpg", "height": 860, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2015/11/25/business/25cawley-obit-1/25cawley-obit-1-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 1513, "width": 1801, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2015/11/25/business/25cawley-obit-1/25cawley-obit-1-thumbSta